Accumulo Backing for Lucene
===========================

Project Team:

- Chris White (chriswhite199)
- Mark Dooley

Overview
========

Loosely based upon the infoq.com document http://www.infoq.com/articles/LuceneHbase, this is an attempt to port this approach to using Accumulo (http://incubator.apache.org/accumulo/) as the backend for a Lucene Index (http://lucene.apache.org) 
